609
00:26:25,106 --> 00:26:26,465
Don't start trouble here!

610
00:26:26,505 --> 00:26:27,346
Stop fighting!

611
00:26:36,146 --> 00:26:36,646
Get lost!

612
00:26:36,985 --> 00:26:37,485
Get lost!

613
00:26:37,705 --> 00:26:38,225
Leave!

614
00:26:38,586 --> 00:26:39,086
Leave!

615
00:26:41,785 --> 00:26:42,586
You brats!

616
00:26:42,866 --> 00:26:43,906
Listen up!

617
00:26:44,305 --> 00:26:47,465
