as soon as possible.

637
00:27:38,186 --> 00:27:39,626
Okay. Goodbye.

638
00:27:43,426 --> 00:27:44,025
How's it going?

639
00:27:44,965 --> 00:27:45,465
Ready now?

640
00:27:45,465 --> 00:27:46,305
Almost done.

641
00:27:51,586 --> 00:27:52,186
Oh my.

642
00:27:52,225 --> 00:27:54,586
One disaster after another!

643
00:27:54,705 --> 00:27:55,465
Your dad's fault.

644
00:27:55,745 --> 00:27:57,586
He can only mess things up.

645
00:27:57,985 --> 00:28:00,346
If he hadn't come,
we'd have the money ready by now.

646
00:28:01,626 --> 00:28:04,312
By the way, did you tell the workers
to bring more people?

647
00:28:04,312 --> 00:28:06,106
