648
00:28:06,505 --> 00:28:07,225
I told them.

649
00:28:08,065 --> 00:28:08,586
Mom.

650
00:28:08,985 --> 00:28:11,745
Didn't you promise Dad
you wouldn't buy the machines?

651
00:28:12,346 --> 00:28:13,465
Just saying.

652
00:28:13,705 --> 00:28:15,106
Just bring the machines back

653
00:28:15,386 --> 00:28:16,866
