655
00:28:20,225 --> 00:28:20,866
Hurry!

656
00:28:20,926 --> 00:28:21,426
Okay.

657
00:28:21,426 --> 00:28:21,926
Done now?

658
00:28:22,826 --> 00:28:23,346
