665
00:28:42,386 --> 00:28:43,586
Force 12?

666
00:28:44,245 --> 00:28:44,745
Yes.

667
00:28:44,745 --> 00:28:46,666
The weather is so fickle!

668
00:28:46,745 --> 00:28:47,465
Thankfully,

669
00:28:47,505 --> 00:28:49,785
Ms. Li applied for this equipment
from the county early.

670
00:28:49,826 --> 00:28:50,705
This is set up.

671
00:28:51,065 --> 00:28:52,785
Typhoon coming! Find shelter!

672
00:28:53,025 --> 00:28:54,346
Typhoon coming! Find shelter!

673
00:28:54,745 --> 00:28:55,666
We'll get it done.

674
00:28:56,265 --> 00:28:57,106
Listen up.

675
00:28:57,785 --> 00:28:59,906
Proceed according to our plan,

676
00:29:00,186 --> 00:29:01,265
and move out separately.

677
00:29:01,826 --> 00:29:03,666
We must protect the people's

678
00:29:03,826 --> 00:29:04,946
