685
00:29:13,202 --> 00:29:16,261
(Yuehai Town People's Government,
The CPC Yuehai Town Committee)

686
00:29:19,218 --> 00:29:20,795
Take care.

687
00:29:35,386 --> 00:29:36,225
Hai, Qiang,

688
