689
00:29:37,305 --> 00:29:38,505
They have 56 people.

690
00:29:39,626 --> 00:29:40,146
And us?

691
00:29:40,906 --> 00:29:41,866
How many of us?

692
00:29:42,626 --> 00:29:43,225
30.

693
00:29:43,946 --> 00:29:44,446
Bro.

694
00:29:44,985 --> 00:29:46,626
They have fewer people than us.

695
00:29:47,705 --> 00:29:49,065
I'll take down Yang Xiaohai.

696
00:29:49,505 --> 00:29:50,866
