708
00:30:23,866 --> 00:30:25,545
(Attention! All Yuehai residents,)

709
00:30:25,826 --> 00:30:28,225
(the typhoon will make landfall
twelve hours ahead.)

710
00:30:28,586 --> 00:30:30,505
(Maximum wind speeds
may exceed Force 12.)

711
00:30:30,946 --> 00:30:33,985
(Expected duration is 12 to 72 hours.)

712
00:30:34,225 --> 00:30:36,666
(Please stay indoors
and keep windows and doors shut.)

713
00:30:36,666 --> 00:30:37,166
How's it?

714
00:30:37,545 --> 00:30:38,386
I'm fine, Hai.

715
00:30:40,705 --> 00:30:41,225
Get up.

716
00:30:48,745 --> 00:30:51,505
Hai, let's get to Binhai Road.

717
00:30:52,025 --> 00:30:53,626
