- To make money!

718
00:30:53,985 --> 00:30:55,465
There's a typhoon! Are you crazy?

719
00:30:55,906 --> 00:30:57,545
This is our chance!

720
00:30:57,785 --> 00:30:59,745
How else can we make big money?

721
00:31:02,906 --> 00:31:03,626
Let's go for it!

722
00:31:05,065 --> 00:31:05,565
Okay.

723
00:31:05,866 --> 00:31:06,545
Let's go for it!

724
00:31:07,106 --> 00:31:07,985
Make big money!

725
00:31:11,305 --> 00:31:12,106
Buddies!

726
00:31:12,465 --> 00:31:13,946
Don't mind the typhoon!

727
00:31:14,505 --> 00:31:15,705
Make big money!

728
00:31:16,146 --> 00:31:17,866
Go make big money!

729
00:31:17,946 --> 00:31:18,866
Go make big money!

730
00:31:18,906 --> 00:31:20,305
- Make money!
- Go make money!

731
00:31:20,646 --> 00:31:21,146
Make money!

732
00:31:21,146 --> 00:31:24,705
- Make money!
- Go make big money!

733
00:31:25,745 --> 00:31:26,745
- Let's go.
- Let's go

734
00:31:26,985 --> 00:31:28,745
- Let's go.
- Go make money.

735
00:31:29,985 --> 00:31:30,866
Are we going?

736
00:31:30,906 --> 00:31:31,866
My foot!

737
00:31:32,626 --> 00:31:34,025
Life matters most.

738
00:31:35,065 --> 00:31:36,626
Tell buddies to go back.

739
00:31:39,426 --> 00:31:40,465
Go back!

740
00:31:40,705 --> 00:31:41,666
Back to Wang Village.

741
00:31:50,745 --> 00:31:51,586
Watch your head!

742
00:31:52,065 --> 00:31:53,186
Watch your heads!

743
00:31:54,225 --> 00:31:55,666
Get down!

744
00:31:55,745 --> 00:31:57,186
No. The wind is too strong.

745
00:31:57,305 --> 00:31:57,946
Get down!

746
00:31:59,906 --> 00:32:00,586
Watch your head!

747
00:32:00,946 --> 00:32:01,745
Watch your head!

748
00:32:06,946 --> 00:32:08,265
How much do you charge?

749
00:32:09,025 --> 00:32:09,906
What did you say?

750
00:32:10,265 --> 00:32:11,785
How much price?

751
00:32:12,906 --> 00:32:14,386
How much?

752
00:32:14,426 --> 00:32:15,386
100 yuan per truck.

753
00:32:15,666 --> 00:32:16,745
100 yuan.

754
00:32:16,906 --> 00:32:17,705
100 yuan.

755
00:32:17,906 --> 00:32:18,406
Okay.

756
00:32:18,705 --> 00:32:19,505
100 yuan total.

757
00:32:19,545 --> 00:32:20,186
Move it!

758
00:32:20,225 --> 00:32:21,666
No!

759
00:32:21,785 --> 00:32:23,985
100 yuan per truck.

760
00:32:24,305 --> 00:32:25,586
100 yuan per truck.

761
00:32:25,626 --> 00:32:27,146
100 yuan total.

762
00:32:28,426 --> 00:32:28,926
No.

763
00:32:29,225 --> 00:32:31,386
We have two and a half trucks.

764
00:32:31,586 --> 00:32:33,346
250? Sounds bad.

765
00:32:33,505 --> 00:32:34,225
What?

766
00:32:34,946 --> 00:32:36,065
Then make it 300 yuan.

767
00:32:36,265 --> 00:32:38,146
He said 250 sounds bad.

768
00:32:38,305 --> 00:32:39,146
200 yuan, okay?

769
00:32:39,386 --> 00:32:39,946
200 yuan.

770
00:32:40,025 --> 00:32:41,265
Fine, 200 yuan.

771
00:32:41,305 --> 00:32:42,545
No!

772
00:32:42,626 --> 00:32:43,626
300 yuan.

773
00:32:44,106 --> 00:32:44,785
300 yuan.

774
00:32:44,985 --> 00:32:46,065
