783
00:32:58,065 --> 00:32:58,586
Okay.

784
00:32:58,626 --> 00:32:59,126
300 yuan.

785
00:32:59,146 --> 00:32:59,826
Okay.

786
00:33:00,186 --> 00:33:01,186
Go!

787
00:33:01,346 --> 00:33:02,426
Be careful.

788
00:33:02,586 --> 00:33:03,186
Move it!

789
00:33:04,745 --> 00:33:06,745
You watch your head!

790
00:33:12,225 --> 00:33:15,426
According to notices
from the province and county,

791
00:33:15,906 --> 00:33:18,745
this typhoon has arrived early.

792
00:33:19,106 --> 00:33:20,946
And it's stronger than last year's,

793
00:33:21,545 --> 00:33:23,386
will reach above Force 12.

794
00:33:23,826 --> 00:33:27,586
While the wind has died down,
you need to evacuate now.

795
00:33:27,666 --> 00:33:28,666
Why are you stopping?

796
00:33:29,225 --> 00:33:31,146
You take Hao to go. I have to go home.

797
00:33:31,186 --> 00:33:32,106
I'll come to you soon.

798
00:33:32,426 --> 00:33:34,586
Hao, stay with Grandma. Don't run off.

799
00:33:34,705 --> 00:33:35,785
I will come find you soon.

800
00:33:35,785 --> 00:33:36,745
Why are you going back?

801
00:33:37,106 --> 00:33:38,346
Nothing. Take him.

802
00:33:38,386 --> 00:33:39,465
I'll come find you soon.

803
00:33:39,985 --> 00:33:40,626
Go on.

804
00:33:43,146 --> 00:33:45,025
(Attention! All Yuehai residents,)

805
00:33:45,106 --> 00:33:47,545
(the typhoon will make landfall
twelve hours ahead.)

806
00:33:47,906 --> 00:33:50,146
(Maximum wind speeds
may exceed Force 12.)

807
00:33:50,346 --> 00:33:53,465
(Expected duration is 12 to 72 hours.)

808
00:33:53,745 --> 00:33:56,146
(Please stay indoors
and keep windows and doors shut.)

809
00:34:37,866 --> 00:34:38,786
Evacuate now!

810
00:34:39,906 --> 00:34:41,105
Forget your belongings!

811
00:34:42,266 --> 00:34:43,505
Look out for each other!

812
00:34:43,866 --> 00:34:44,866
See if anyone's missing!

813
00:34:45,625 --> 00:34:46,866
Inform everyone!

814
00:35:03,625 --> 00:35:05,346
Get to shore!

815
00:35:05,625 --> 00:35:06,906
Why are there so many boats?

816
00:35:07,585 --> 00:35:08,312
The wind's coming.

817
00:35:08,426 --> 00:35:09,545
They came to take shelter.

818
00:35:12,545 --> 00:35:15,826
All vessels, follow my orders!

819
00:35:16,152 --> 00:35:18,232
I'm the deputy mayor of Yuehai Town,

820
00:35:18,505 --> 00:35:19,640
Xie Chunlai.

821
00:35:21,048 --> 00:35:22,809
All vessels must dock now!

822
00:35:23,256 --> 00:35:24,736
Dock now!

823
00:35:24,914 --> 00:35:27,861
This typhoon is extremely dangerous.

824
00:35:28,263 --> 00:35:30,359
Secure your boats properly!

825
00:35:30,498 --> 00:35:33,455
Evacuate the harbor now!

826
00:35:36,386 --> 00:35:38,386
The typhoon's here! Stop working!

827
00:35:38,665 --> 00:35:39,585
Evacuate now!

828
00:35:39,866 --> 00:35:41,786
Don't go anywhere. Go back now!

829
00:35:41,946 --> 00:35:43,226
Evacuate now!

830
00:35:44,105 --> 00:35:45,826
Everyone, get back now!

831
00:35:46,426 --> 00:35:47,665
Everyone, evacuate now!

832
00:35:47,866 --> 00:35:49,185
Go back! Don't go anywhere!

833
00:35:49,346 --> 00:35:50,706
You're still working?

834
00:35:50,746 --> 00:35:51,746
Stop working! Get going!

835
00:35:58,545 --> 00:35:59,045
(Come.)

836
00:35:59,545 --> 00:36:00,386
It'll be our house.

837
00:36:00,746 --> 00:36:02,625
This big space here...

838
00:36:03,346 --> 00:36:05,185
We'll turn it into the living room.

839
00:36:05,306 --> 00:36:06,386
This will be the bedroom.

840
00:36:07,386 --> 00:36:08,426
This will be the study.

841
00:36:12,746 --> 00:36:13,306
Open wider.

842
00:36:13,505 --> 00:36:14,145
- Wider.
- What?

843
00:36:14,145 --> 00:36:15,346
There seems to be some...

844
00:36:16,946 --> 00:36:18,145
This will be our home.

845
00:36:18,266 --> 00:36:18,946
Make a mark.

846
00:36:27,906 --> 00:36:29,426
(We've been together for ten years.)

847
00:36:30,266 --> 00:36:32,386
I've been trying
to cut the long distance between us.

848
00:36:32,985 --> 00:36:34,826
But why are there
always so many obstacles?

849
00:36:35,386 --> 00:36:36,585
Now, you've come to Yuehai.

850
00:36:36,906 --> 00:36:39,426
I understand you have your dreams
and ambitions to pursue here.

851
00:36:39,505 --> 00:36:41,105
But what about my dreams and ambitions?

852
00:36:54,906 --> 00:36:58,145
(Residents of Yuehai, for your safety,)

853
00:36:58,346 --> 00:37:00,426
(please proceed to the safe zone.)

854
00:37:00,826 --> 00:37:02,665
(Keep the windows and doors shut.
Stay inside.)

855
00:37:04,465 --> 00:37:05,065
Stop it!

856
00:37:05,426 --> 00:37:07,386
This typhoon is unusually severe!

857
00:37:07,645 --> 00:37:08,145
Stop it!

858
00:37:08,145 --> 00:37:09,065
Safety first!

859
00:37:09,105 --> 00:37:10,226
Let's head back, okay?

860
00:37:10,985 --> 00:37:11,826
Don't go anywhere.

861
00:37:11,866 --> 00:37:12,786
Go back.

862
00:37:13,866 --> 00:37:15,346
Evacuate! Get everyone back!

863
00:37:15,665 --> 00:37:18,346
Water and food supplies
are fully stocked.

864
00:37:18,505 --> 00:37:20,226
Do not go out alone!

865
00:37:20,465 --> 00:37:21,985
If anyone is missing,

866
00:37:22,266 --> 00:37:22,906
tell them

867
00:37:23,025 --> 00:37:24,025
to register, okay?

868
00:37:24,266 --> 00:37:26,145
Tan!

869
00:37:26,266 --> 00:37:26,946
Here!

870
00:37:27,185 --> 00:37:27,746
Tan!

871
00:37:27,985 --> 00:37:28,706
Get inside.

872
00:37:28,766 --> 00:37:29,266
Let's go!

873
00:37:29,266 --> 00:37:29,766
Hurry!

874
00:37:29,786 --> 00:37:31,185
Tan, I've got 15 people with me.

875
00:37:31,306 --> 00:37:32,386
Where should we put them?

876
00:37:32,505 --> 00:37:33,185
15 people...

877
00:37:33,505 --> 00:37:34,625
To the canteen.

878
00:37:34,746 --> 00:37:35,585
To the canteen.

879
00:37:35,625 --> 00:37:36,386
Hurry!

880
00:37:40,306 --> 00:37:41,266
Hurry! Come on!

881
00:37:41,465 --> 00:37:42,185
Move! Make way!

882
00:37:42,306 --> 00:37:43,266
Where were you?

883
00:37:43,465 --> 00:37:44,665
Be careful.

884
00:37:44,706 --> 00:37:45,746
Take it easy.

885
00:37:46,105 --> 00:37:46,665
Call Mr. Lin.

886
00:37:46,776 --> 00:37:47,386
Call Mr. Lin.

887
00:37:47,386 --> 00:37:48,185
Mr. Lin.

888
00:37:48,665 --> 00:37:49,465
Be careful. Easy.

889
00:37:50,105 --> 00:37:50,746
Lin!

890
00:37:52,446 --> 00:37:52,946
Ms. Xiao.

891
00:37:52,946 --> 00:37:53,625
Get him water.

892
00:37:53,625 --> 00:37:54,185
Don't worry.

893
00:37:54,266 --> 00:37:54,840
What's wrong?

894
00:37:55,105 --> 00:37:58,346
Yan ran back home. I couldn't stop her.

895
00:37:58,625 --> 00:37:59,706
Yan ran back home?

896
00:38:03,545 --> 00:38:04,505
There's space here.

897
00:38:05,105 --> 00:38:05,605
Okay.

898
00:38:07,985 --> 00:38:08,946
Lend me your bike.

899
00:38:25,585 --> 00:38:26,306
Who is there?

900
00:38:27,386 --> 00:38:29,706
Why aren't you evacuated yet?
Seeking death?

901
00:38:30,866 --> 00:38:31,786
The stuff...

902
00:38:40,346 --> 00:38:40,946
Gao Xuemei!

903
00:38:48,346 --> 00:38:49,386
What are you doing here?

904
00:38:59,346 --> 00:39:00,665
You didn't return the machine?

905
00:39:01,426 --> 00:39:03,426
I couldn't bear to return
such a good new machine.

906
00:39:04,465 --> 00:39:06,706
Xie, do something.

907
00:39:06,946 --> 00:39:08,706
The moving workers all ran off!

908
00:39:09,226 --> 00:39:10,665
We must get the machine back.

909
00:39:10,906 --> 00:39:12,826
If this 500,000-yuan machine sinks,

910
00:39:13,105 --> 00:39:14,105
we're all doomed.

911
00:39:14,306 --> 00:39:16,465
Xie, do something now!

912
00:39:18,105 --> 00:39:18,665
What?

913
00:39:19,585 --> 00:39:20,866
Stop dragging me. What?

914
00:39:20,866 --> 00:39:21,465
How dare you!

915
00:39:21,826 --> 00:39:22,386
I'm staying!

916
00:39:22,545 --> 00:39:23,045
Go back!

917
00:39:23,185 --> 00:39:25,185
I have to be with the machine.

918
00:39:26,266 --> 00:39:27,226
Fatty!

919
00:39:28,226 --> 00:39:29,306
Fatty!

920
00:39:29,985 --> 00:39:31,105
Fatty! Terrible!

921
00:39:31,386 --> 00:39:32,025
What's wrong?

922
00:39:32,065 --> 00:39:34,665
Mom's machine is stuck at the dock.
We don't have enough workers.

923
00:39:34,706 --> 00:39:36,706
Mom told me to get more people
to move the machine back.

924
00:39:36,706 --> 00:39:37,465
Okay, I see.

925
00:39:37,706 --> 00:39:39,346
Look, kid, see?

926
00:39:39,625 --> 00:39:41,025
That's cash! Money!

927
00:39:41,226 --> 00:39:42,426
I want to help.

928
00:39:42,545 --> 00:39:43,706
But after we finish

929
00:39:43,946 --> 00:39:46,386
moving this stuff, okay?

930
00:39:46,625 --> 00:39:47,386
Just wait.

931
00:39:47,386 --> 00:39:48,946
My mom is still waiting at the dock!

932
00:39:49,665 --> 00:39:50,426
Fatty!

933
00:39:50,545 --> 00:39:51,045
Xiaoyu!

934
00:39:51,585 --> 00:39:53,946
You said Ms. Gao's machine
is stuck at the dock?

935
00:39:54,545 --> 00:39:55,505
Can you get there?

936
00:39:55,665 --> 00:39:56,545
I can pay more.

937
00:39:56,826 --> 00:39:57,465
Hold on.

938
00:39:57,786 --> 00:39:58,426
Qiang.

939
00:39:58,946 --> 00:39:59,505
Qiang.

940
00:39:59,826 --> 00:40:00,386
Let's go.

941
00:40:00,625 --> 00:40:01,706
Where are we going, Hai?

942
00:40:01,746 --> 00:40:02,465
To the dock.

943
00:40:02,746 --> 00:40:04,746
Ms. Gao's machine is stuck at the dock.

944
00:40:04,866 --> 00:40:07,545
Can't go, Hai. We're swamped here.

945
00:40:07,706 --> 00:40:09,065
Ms. Gao helped us before.

946
00:40:09,105 --> 00:40:11,185
Our first earnings came from Ms. Gao.

947
00:40:11,266 --> 00:40:13,946
She paid us money,
and we provided the labor. We're even.

948
00:40:14,266 --> 00:40:15,625
We really can't go, Hai.

949
00:40:18,346 --> 00:40:19,625
Fine.

950
00:40:19,706 --> 00:40:21,366
We agreed. No refunds.

951
00:40:21,706 --> 00:40:22,505
So you're not going?

952
00:40:22,985 --> 00:40:23,985
Then you stay here.

953
00:40:25,226 --> 00:40:25,726
It's fine.

954
00:40:25,946 --> 00:40:27,025
Xiaoyu, I'll go.

955
00:40:27,426 --> 00:40:28,465
I'll go with you.

956
00:40:28,505 --> 00:40:30,505
Don't. It's dangerous. Go home now.

957
00:40:32,266 --> 00:40:33,426
Then you must help my mom

958
00:40:33,665 --> 00:40:34,906
and get her machine back.

959
00:40:34,946 --> 00:40:35,746
Let's go. Come on!

960
00:40:36,065 --> 00:40:37,266
- Okay, coming!
- Let's go!

961
00:40:37,706 --> 00:40:39,866
Xiaohai, be careful.

962
00:40:39,946 --> 00:40:41,505
Go home!

963
00:40:46,906 --> 00:40:49,185
You even abandon me for the machine?

964
00:40:49,545 --> 00:40:50,585
You abandon our family?

965
00:40:50,625 --> 00:40:51,306
Let go!

966
00:40:53,185 --> 00:40:53,985
Want to get killed?

967
00:40:54,306 --> 00:40:54,866
Yes!

968
00:40:55,145 --> 00:40:55,866
What do you want?

969
00:40:55,866 --> 00:40:56,985
I want the machine.

970
00:40:57,665 --> 00:40:58,165
Fine.

971
00:40:58,826 --> 00:41:00,085
I'll help you, okay?

972
00:41:00,346 --> 00:41:01,346
We move it now.

973
00:41:01,906 --> 00:41:02,746
Want to get killed?

974
00:41:03,145 --> 00:41:04,585
Then I'll die with you.

975
00:41:04,826 --> 00:41:06,105
If you die, I'll die with you.

976
00:41:06,746 --> 00:41:08,025
We're family.

977
00:41:08,426 --> 00:41:09,706
Go move it now!

978
00:41:11,826 --> 00:41:12,426
Okay?

979
00:41:24,386 --> 00:41:24,946
Xie.

980
00:41:26,025 --> 00:41:27,545
It's so hard for us to get

981
00:41:28,306 --> 00:41:29,266
where we are now.

982
00:41:29,906 --> 00:41:31,105
We've had it so tough.

983
00:41:32,746 --> 00:41:35,065
No way back means only a way out,
understand?

984
00:41:37,906 --> 00:41:39,065
Ms. Gao.

985
00:41:39,706 --> 00:41:40,786
Ms. Gao.

986
00:41:41,346 --> 00:41:42,906
We're here to help you.

987
00:41:43,505 --> 00:41:45,226
Don't! Go back!

988
00:41:46,906 --> 00:41:47,426
What?

989
00:41:48,025 --> 00:41:48,866
Go back!

990
00:41:49,306 --> 00:41:50,505
Don't stay!

991
00:41:50,505 --> 00:41:51,226
Xie Chunlai!

992
00:41:51,346 --> 00:41:51,846
Go back.

993
00:41:52,185 --> 00:41:53,185
- What do you want?
- Go back!

994
00:41:53,266 --> 00:41:56,505
They're here. Just let them move it.

995
00:41:56,545 --> 00:41:58,065
I'm the head of this household.

996
00:41:58,465 --> 00:41:59,746
They follow my orders.

997
00:41:59,946 --> 00:42:01,946
Want everyone to get killed with you?

998
00:42:02,226 --> 00:42:03,226
Can they even move it?

999
00:42:03,346 --> 00:42:04,105
Look at the sky.

1000
00:42:05,665 --> 00:42:08,306
The typhoon's coming soon, Gao Xuemei!

1001
00:42:08,786 --> 00:42:10,985
That boat is tied securely.

1002
00:42:11,706 --> 00:42:14,746
The cargo's anchored,
and wind won't move it.

1003
00:42:15,226 --> 00:42:16,145
It'll be fine.

1004
00:42:16,346 --> 00:42:18,306
Xuemei, listen to me.

1005
00:42:18,746 --> 00:42:21,545
Just wait till the typhoon passes.

1006
00:42:21,625 --> 00:42:23,946
Even the fiercest storm
passes eventually.

1007
00:42:24,706 --> 00:42:25,985
We'll come and move

1008
00:42:26,025 --> 00:42:28,746
the machine home together, okay?

1009
00:42:28,965 --> 00:42:29,906
- Then...
- Okay?

1010
00:42:29,906 --> 00:42:31,826
That costs 500,000 yuan, Xie.

1011
00:42:31,906 --> 00:42:34,025
Life matters most.
You matter most to me.

1012
00:42:34,826 --> 00:42:36,946
Xuemei, as long as we're alive,

1013
00:42:38,346 --> 00:42:39,346
we can earn everything.

1014
00:42:40,585 --> 00:42:41,746
If that machine's gone,

1015
00:42:42,266 --> 00:42:43,826
even if it's five million,

1016
00:42:44,426 --> 00:42:45,786
I'll let you buy a new one. Deal?

1017
00:42:46,185 --> 00:42:47,426
Go back with me now. Please?

1018
00:42:47,625 --> 00:42:49,625
Promise me the machine will be safe.

1019
00:42:49,906 --> 00:42:52,306
Typhoon's hitting any minute.
Move it or not?

1020
00:42:53,386 --> 00:42:53,906
Come!

1021
00:42:54,625 --> 00:42:55,386
Let's go!

1022
00:42:58,226 --> 00:43:01,746
My machine!

1023
00:43:06,280 --> 00:43:10,990
♪Gently holding your face♪

1024
00:43:13,340 --> 00:43:18,588
♪To dry the tears from your eyes♪

1025
00:43:20,148 --> 00:43:25,341
♪My heart will always be yours♪

1026
00:43:27,156 --> 00:43:32,492
♪Tell me you'll never be alone again♪

1027
00:43:34,120 --> 00:43:38,108
♪Gazing deep into your eyes♪

1028
00:43:41,028 --> 00:43:46,397
♪No further words are needed♪

1029
00:43:48,033 --> 00:43:53,238
♪Tightly holding your hand♪

1030
00:43:54,972 --> 00:44:00,332
♪The warmth has never changed♪

1031
00:44:01,448 --> 00:44:04,556
♪We share the joy♪

1032
00:44:04,884 --> 00:44:08,108
♪We share the pain♪

1033
00:44:08,362 --> 00:44:13,933
♪We hold the same hope deep inside♪

1034
00:44:15,373 --> 00:44:18,372
♪We brave the storm♪

1035
00:44:18,892 --> 00:44:21,884
♪We share the quest♪

1036
00:44:22,325 --> 00:44:28,268
♪We cherish this love we share♪

1037
00:44:31,458 --> 00:44:36,514
♪Whether we've ever met before♪

1038
00:44:38,419 --> 00:44:43,829
♪Be it near or far away♪

1039
00:44:45,420 --> 00:44:50,603
♪My heartfelt wish for you♪

1040
00:44:52,387 --> 00:44:57,517
♪Is for your peace and happiness♪

1041
00:44:58,824 --> 00:45:01,994
♪We share the joy♪

1042
00:45:02,252 --> 00:45:05,320
♪We share the pain♪

1043
00:45:05,744 --> 00:45:11,967
♪We hold the same hope deep inside♪

1044
00:45:12,567 --> 00:45:15,630
♪We brave the storm♪

1045
00:45:15,966 --> 00:45:19,054
♪We share the quest♪

1046
00:45:19,350 --> 00:45:25,527
♪We cherish this love we share♪
